2a + 4b + 3c = 5.60
a + b + 2c = 2.60
\left(\matrix{ 3 & 2 & 4 \\ 2 & 4 & 3 \\ 1 & 1 & 2}\right) \left(\matrix{a\\b\\c}\right) = \left( \matrix{5.85 \\ 5.60 \\ 2.60} \right)
